&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-14219&quot; title=&quot;OverseerSolrResponse&amp;#39;s serialVersionUID has changed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-14219&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-14219&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Revert changes in OverseerSolrRespose and move serialization (#1227)&lt;/p&gt;

